  "prompt": "My boyfriend dumped me . I am totally lost and I have no idea what to do ,as if I have forgotten myself . How should I restart my life, again?",
  "response": "I'm sorry to hear about your breakup. Here are some steps to help you restart and heal:\n\n1. Allow yourself to grieve\n- Feel your emotions\n- Cry if you need to\n- Don't suppress your feelings\n\n2. Self-care is crucial\n- Get enough sleep\n- Eat healthy\n- Exercise regularly\n- Practice meditation or yoga\n\n3. Reconnect with yourself\n- Rediscover your interests and hobbies\n- Set personal goals\n- Focus on self-improvement\n- Spend time with supportive friends and family\n\n4. Emotional healing\n- Consider talking to a therapist\n- Journal your feelings\n- Practice positive self-talk\n- Avoid blaming yourself\n\n5. Avoid unhealthy coping mechanisms\n- Don't jump into a new relationship immediately\n- Limit contact with your ex\n- Avoid excessive drinking or destructive behaviors\n\n6. Personal growth\n- Learn from the experience\n- Build self-confidence\n- Try new experiences\n- Develop new skills\n\n7. Stay positive\n- Believe in yourself\n- Understand that healing takes time\n- Know that you deserve happiness\n\nRemember, this is a process. Be patient and kind to yourself. You will get through this and emerge stronger.\n\nWould you like to discuss any specific concerns or feelings you're experiencing?",
